# A solo maintainer cannot approve their own pull request, so enabling "Require review from Code
# Owners" would make every gate-layer PR un-mergeable except by admin override — training exactly the
# reflex this governance exists to prevent. Enforcement is the `gate-review` REQUIRED STATUS CHECK,
# which a solo owner CAN satisfy (by producing the independent review record) without a second human.
# See CONTRIBUTING.md "Governance".
